  | Sospeso interval | Between action and verification | The action has been taken (at p < 0.95) but outcome is not yet verified. System is in жњЄзџҐ. |
  | futon3c pre-implementation | ARGUMENT written, exotype validated, no code | The social loop is specified but not instantiated. Non-equilibrium: the argument creates obligations the code hasn't satisfied. |
  | Context boundary | Between session compaction and new turn | The LLM has lost detailed context but retains summary. Actionable but not fully predictable. |

  == 5. THE FUTONIC LOOP IN PRACTICE ==

  The abstract loop (В§3) maps onto three concrete cycles:

  5.1 PSRв†’PUR cycle (per-task):

  (futonic-loop
    (input   и±Ў  := task request entering the gate pipeline)
    (choose  йѓЁ  := select decomposition: which gate, which timescale)
    (articulate е’… := write PSR: choose a pattern, commit to an approach)
    (if (forms й№Ѕ) := pattern (й№µ) + evidence shape (зљї) compose)
    (and (sense й¦™) := during execution, perceive whether it's working)
    (and (regulate рџ”®) := stay within budget, reject if budget exceeded)
    (then
      (act-within жњЄзџҐ := execute under uncertainty)
      (evaluate е‘і := write PUR: evaluate outcome by felt difference))
    (else
      (apply жЌЁ := reject at gate, park mission, write PAR)))

  5.2 Derivation xenotype (per-mission):

  (futonic-loop
    (input   и±Ў  := domain to be derived: "social coordination")
    (choose  йѓЁ  := IDENTIFY the decomposition regime: git archaeology,
                    pattern audit, devmap review)
    (articulate е’… := MAP + DERIVE: articulate patterns and requirements
                    from the evidence)
    (if (forms й№Ѕ) := ARGUE: requirements (й№µ) + argument structure (зљї)
                    compose into a valid case)
    (and (sense й¦™) := during argument construction, perceive convergences)
    (and (regulate рџ”®) := VERIFY: check invariants, validate diagrams)
    (then
      (act-within жњЄзџҐ := INSTANTIATE: build the code)
      (evaluate е‘і := tests pass, 8/8 checks, round-trip proof))
    (else
      (apply жЌЁ := park mission, record blocker, explicit exit)))

  5.3 Glacial loop (per-library-evolution):

  (futonic-loop
    (input   и±Ў  := accumulated proof paths from many tasks)
    (choose  йѓЁ  := L1-observe: which tension criterion to scan?
                    structural-irritation / pre-symbolic-pressure /
                    trans-situational-reappearance)
    (articulate е’… := name the tension: a recurring pattern emerges)
    (if (forms й№Ѕ) := tension observation (й№µ) + flexiarg format (зљї)
                    compose into a candidate pattern)
    (and (sense й¦™) := does this tension appear across contexts?)
    (and (regulate рџ”®) := does it meet the canonicalization threshold?
                    frequency >= 3, contexts >= 2)
    (then
      (act-within жњЄзџҐ := write new flexiarg to library)
      (evaluate е‘і := subsequent G3 accepts the new pattern))
    (else
      (apply жЌЁ := tension does not meet threshold, record but do not
                    canonicalize)))

